N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 5012.7 - Chances of winning

State Regulations
(a) First prize. Five winning numbers in one game panel. Chances of winning: 1 in
575,757. (b) Second prize. Any four
winning numbers in one game panel. Chances of winning: 1 in 3,387. (c) Third prize. Any three winning numbers in
one game panel. Chances of winning: 1 in 103. (d) Fourth prize. Any two winning numbers in
one game panel. Chances of winning: 1 in 9.6. Overall chances of winning a
prize for a $1 bet: 1 in 8.77. Notes
